---
import HeaderLayout from '../../layouts/HeaderLayout.astro'
import GalleryContainer from '../../components/GalleryContainer'
import games from '../../utils/games.json'
const screenshots = games.io.screenshots
import './styles.scss'
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
		<link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Nakazawa Titles - I/O</title>
		<meta name="description" content='And thus begins the revision of "the world"————.' />
		<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
		<meta property="og:title" content="Nakazawa Titles - I/O" />
		<meta property="og:description" content='And thus begins the revision of "the world"————.' />
		<meta property="og:url" content="https://infinityseri.es/" />
		<meta property="og:image" content="https://infinityseri.es/io_banner_horizontal.webp" />
		<meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
		<meta property="twitter:url" content="https://infinityseri.es/" />
		<meta property="twitter:title" content="Nakazawa Titles - I/O" />
		<meta property="twitter:description" content='And thus begins the revision of "the world"————.' />
		<meta property="twitter:image" content="https://infinityseri.es/io_banner_horizontal.webp" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<HeaderLayout>
			<div class="io">
				<div class="info">
					<div class="cover">
						<picture>
							<source srcset='/io_banner_vertical.avif' type='image/avif' media='(width >= 950px)' />
							<source srcset='/io_banner_vertical.webp' type='image/webp' media='(width >= 950px)' />
							<source srcset='/io_banner_horizontal.avif' type='image/avif' media='(width < 950px)' />
							<img src="/io_banner_horizontal.webp" alt="" />
						</picture>
					</div>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="title">
							<span>アイオー</span>
							<h2>I/O revision II</h2>
							<div class="date">January 26, 2006</div>
						</div>
						<div class="downloads">
							<h3>Downloads</h3>
							<div class="section">
								<span>Base game:</span>
								<ul>
									<li>I/O revision II <a href="https://archive.org/download/io-revision-ii/io-revision-ii_archive.torrent" target="_blank">[Torrent]</a> <a href="https://archive.org/download/io-revision-ii/%EF%BC%A9%EF%BC%8F%EF%BC%AF%E2%80%90revision%E2%85%A1.7z" target="_blank">[Direct]</a></li>
									<span>Make sure to run "ioregadd.bat", because the game needs to modify some registry stuff to work properly.</span>
								</ul>
							</div>
							<div class="section">
								<span>Locale Emulator (mandatory):</span>
								<ul>
									<li><a href="https://github.com/xupefei/Locale-Emulator/releases/download/v2.5.0.1/Locale.Emulator.2.5.0.1.zip" target='_blank'>Locale Emulator</a></li>
									<span>You need to right click on the game executable and select "Locale Emulator > Run in Japanese".</span>
									<span>You can skip the locale emulator if you already have a way to run Japanese games on your computer.</span>
								</ul>
							</div>
							<div class="section">
								<span>Upscaler (recommended):</span>
								<ul>
									<li><a href="https://github.com/Blinue/Magpie/releases" target='_blank'>Magpie</a></li>
									<span>CuNNy model is recommended for better results, but if you don't want to use an AI upscaler you can always use something like Lanczos.</span>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="guide">
							<h3>Guide (required)</h3>
							<div class="section">
								<ul>
									<li><a href="https://namenotdecided.home.blog/2021/10/24/i-o-spoiler-free-guide/" target='_blank'>Cred Fire (Double Eyepatch) - Spoiler-Free Guide</a></li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="moreInfo">
					<h2>More information</h2>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="section">
							<h3>Description</h3>
							<div class="description">
								<p>April 26th, 2032 A.D. - Megalopolis Tokyo - 12:12 in the morning.</p>
								<p></p>
								<p>A total lunar eclipse occurs for the first time in 3 years. Even though it's supposed to be a simple astronomical phenomenon, it soon sets off a series of unexpected events. Unexplainable mysteries, terrorist incidents, and network crime surge as if in unison. The truth mixes with lies, as if the world is awake but still sleeping.</p>
								<p></p>
								<p>Something has begun. Somewhere no one can see. Something no one knows about.</p>
								<p></p>
								<p>This is a story of the chance meeting and tragic parting of the young men and women living in this world.</p>
								<p></p>
								<p>And thus...</p>
								<p></p>
								<p>"The beginning is the end, and the end is the beginning"</p>
								<span>[From <a href="https://vndb.org/v96" target='_blank'>VNDB</a>]</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="section">
							<GalleryContainer client:idle gallery={screenshots} title="Screenshots" spoilerText={['(Show spoilers)', '(Hide spoilers)']} />
						</div>
						<div class="section">
							<h3>Opening</h3>
							<div class="video">
								<iframe width="100%" height="auto" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/w4hSVN5Ur_o?si=dsr3eixyT1WdZCcN" title="I/O Opening" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="section">
							<h3>FAQ</h3>
							<div class="questions">
								<div class="question">
									<h4>How do I run the game? There are too many .exe files</h4>
									<p>To run the game you need to execute the "io_r2_en.exe" file through the locale emulator.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="question">
									<h4>How do I use Magpie?</h4>
									<p>First you need to start Magpie by double clicking the .exe file. Once Magpie is open you need to select a scaling factor (for this game 3x is recommended) and a scaling model. As mentioned above, CuNNy is highly recommended, but if you don't want to use an AI model you can use Lanczos.</p>
									<p>After everything is configured properly, you can start the game (in windowed mode) and press the shortcut "Alt+Shift+Q" to activate the upscaling. With that done, a menu should appear on the top with a bunch of options, just select the option to play in fullscreen.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</HeaderLayout>
	</body>
</html>
